overview: A story about a paranormal entity whom took over the responsibility of caring for a baby from its irresponsible parents.  Sara (Emma Maembong) had to reclaim Murni (Putri Iesya) from a supernatural entity that had been taking care of Murni since she was a child. Nyang, determined to take over Murni from Sara after seeing Murni neglected by her own parents.
title: Nyang
